{
  "stem": "4753.9",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we didn't allow to either of us to come too low and give up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had-- I have my girlfriend in New York, who had an aunt in New York at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after the war, she wanted-- Gizko, her name-- to go to America.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she said she doesn't go-- just if I will be able to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I did receive the papers, also, to come to America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did I tell you that before?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because she-- in-- in Braunschweig, where we were-- that is another city in Germany when we came out from-- we were brought out from Auschwitz by the SS men to Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did go there to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And her 10 toes and fingers were frozen and raw, very painful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she one day didn't want to come to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I wrapped her arm around mine arm, and I was pulling through the whole-- I don't know how many kilometers we were going to the working place-- with me, because I didn't want it to leave her behind.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one day, she didn't come, because she really couldn't anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was sent to the so-called hospital, where they were just collecting people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when you go on to the hospital, you never did return.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I came back from work, and I asked, where is my friend, Gizko, they said she's next door in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a separate building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when that was dark-- all day, that was air raid, but evening especially.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when that pitch dark, I came out from the place where I supposed to sleep, gone through a big hall where we every morning counted, in that time, and gone to the next house.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the door, there was an SS man standing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
